{"id": "1432220263747031151", "channel_id": "1432220263747031151", "type": 0, "author_id": "686916856812273665", "author_name": "ntktooyah", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hello i just joined the game recently, my current account is like shown and im using the shown team also. I still can't do the first stages of \"Everbright Nightfall\" event. How should i build my team and who should i aim for, should i continue pulling Aequor on \"Realm Study\" or should i pull for wheels now?", "timestamp": "2025-10-27T04:12:00.243000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1432220264233566268", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1312557, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1432220263747031151/1432220264233566268/image.png?ex=69cc9b10&is=69cb4990&hm=6ac1e9bb40c90ff21211e6480d2ad529f8aa1cad5f7707f6c7a3d69c45ef9d53&"}, {"id": "1432220264673841273", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1247152, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1432220263747031151/1432220264673841273/image.png?ex=69cc9b10&is=69cb4990&hm=d8aa03d069d372a3bb967c9ebfc993d30a5c839696740d1521d6936cc59c4d54&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432220263747031151", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Lost new player", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1432480228680400947", "channel_id": "1432220263747031151", "type": 0, "author_id": "248551659771265026", "author_name": "unicorned_batman", "author_bot": false, "content": "The team you're using right now is solid and should get you far. Eventually you'd want to switch out Celeste for Hemeln the second you get him. Goliath spot can be flex between Goliath, Nautila and GDoll depending on your needs\nUse your dupe from the monthly shop on Tawil until you get her +4.\nYou should pull a little bit more on realm study, until you get caecus on E3. It's not mandatory and if you're super unlucky and get everything but him, you should switch to wheels regardless and use a pyramid on someone like Faros and use the dupes from there to E3 your Caecus.\n\nThe event stages are decently hard for new players, especially since it has a different ruleset. The way I've done it when I started out was pick every defensive option like Sanga and Nautila and get a Whaled out GDoll from the friend support. I then relied on emergency gnosis to clear it once and then just used auto clear for the tickets.", "timestamp": "2025-10-27T21:25:00.713000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-27T21:25:29.298000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1432220263747031151", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Lost new player", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747463379390545", "1400747489132412979", "1400747088995811358"]}
